{ lib, buildRosPackage, fetchurl, ament-cmake, ament-cmake-gtest, ament-cmake-pytest, ament-lint-auto, ament-lint-common, launch, launch-ros, launch-testing, nav2-common, navigation2, slam-toolbox }:
